=================================================== 
MX @ → mx1.hostinger.com (priority 10)
MX @ → mx2.hostinger.com (priority 20)
================================================== 
1. User enters phone → clicks "Get OTP on WhatsApp"
2. Backend generates OTP → stores it
3. WhatsApp opens with message:
   "FROOTZE OTP 9448102615"
4. User SENDS that message to 919513430615
5. Nalamini WhatsApp bot receives it
6. Bot calls frootze backend → backend returns OTP
7. Bot replies to user: "Your frootze OTP is 485729. Valid 10 mins."
8. User enters OTP on screen → logged in ✅
